National, regional and global mortality due to alcoholic cardiomyopathy in 2015.

Manthey J(1), Probst C(1)(2), Rylett M(2), Rehm J(1)(2)(3)(4)(5)(6).

Author information:
(1)Institute for Clinical Psychology and Psychotherapy, TU Dresden, Dresden, 
Germany.
(2)Institute for Mental Health Policy Research, Centre for Addiction and Mental 
Health, Toronto, Ontario, Canada.
(3)Campbell Family Mental Health Research Institute, Centre for Addiction and 
Mental Health, Toronto, Ontario, Canada.
(4)Institute of Medical Science (IMS), University of Toronto, Toronto, Ontario, 
