Erratum in
    JAMA. 2018 May 1;319(17 ):1824.

Comment in
    JAMA. 2018 Mar 13;319(10 ):988-990.
    JAMA. 2018 Mar 13;319(10 ):983-985.
    JAMA. 2018 Mar 13;319(10):986-987.
    JAMA. 2018 Mar 13;319(10 ):990-992.
    Nat Genet. 2018 Apr;50(4):473.
